video_title: 2 More Days ... Till Our Psych2Go Event in Irvine California (Oct 14th)
transcript:
hey guys it's Jay with narus Clinic
Michelle from Psy to go and Matt from
The narus Clinic Foundation letting you
know that on Saturday October 14th from
3:00 to 7:00 p.m. we are going to be
hosting coffee and books for mental
health here at the Barnes & Noble in
Irvine Spectrum anything you buy in the
store or the cafe part of the proceeds
go to the newus clinic foundation and
accessible and affordable mental
healthare so if you have some time
Friday October 14th don't forget to
check us out 3 to 7 see youall there
